text: Kenkichi Ishiguro (born 10 August 1946) is a Japanese equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Japan Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
